                            <comment id="17448724" author="jira-bot" created="Wed, 24 Nov 2021 16:48:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1895301 from Tilman Hausherr in branch &apos;pdfbox/branches/2.0&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
